dct_title_s: Virginiae item et Floridae Americae provinciarum, nova descriptio
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Map by Hondius, from a Dutch edition of Mercator's Atlas, with text on verso for "Virginia ende Floridae," p. 383 and 384. Signature: 8.X. Includes notes, ill., and cartouche with a view of a Florida Indian village on the left, and a Virginia Indian village on the right.
